\par\par \b \uc2 Govt draws up  \highlight22\uc2 economic \highlight\uc2  action plan for 2004   \b0\par\par\uc2 Fabiola Desy Unidjaja/Dadan Wijaksana, The Jakarta Post, Jakarta   \par \uc2 552 \uc2 words\par \uc2 6 January 2004\par \uc2 The Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par 3\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2004 The Jakarta Post   \par \par \uc2 The current government, whose term will end in 10 months, has vowed to improve the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  this year by capitalizing on improved \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  momentum worldwide to counter possible \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2  resulting from nationwide elections.   \par \par \uc2 Improving \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  performance would remain the focus of the government, and the government planned to do its best to keep the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  from being disrupted by the election process, Coordinating Minister for the \b \highlight22\uc2 Economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  Dorodjatun Kuntjoro-Jakti said on Monday.   \par \par \uc2 "The election is not an excuse to neglect the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , especially when we see various signs of a recovery worldwide. Many have predicted that the pace of an \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  turn-around would increase this year," he announced after a Cabinet meeting -- the first this year -- with the main agenda of laying down guidelines for the government to manage the country's \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  throughout the year.   \par \par \uc2 Dorodjatun said that generating higher \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth would be the highest priority. The government hopes to achieve this mainly by improving the country's business competitiveness.   \par \par \uc2 "The only way to improve competitiveness is by addressing problems hampering exports and investment performance. Those tasks will be carried out by respective teams," he said, referring to the two teams consisting of Cabinet ministers set up to formulate ways to boost exports and investment performance.   \par \par \uc2 He did not give details about how to resolve those problems but various reports have noted that drawing up a competitive \b \highlight22\uc2 tax policy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , continued reform in the customs office, reducing labor-related conflicts and promoting legal certainty were all among the priorities to be quickly addressed.   \par \par \uc2 All those have become contributing factors to the country's lower-than-expected \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth over the years as rapid recovery in exports and investment performance has remained hard to come by, thus stalling efforts to reduce poverty and unemployment.   \par \par \uc2 Dorodjatun admitted that there had been slow progress in the fight against poverty and unemployment, saying it was the result of a difficulties in translating a sound and improving macroeconomic climate to the various microeconomic sectors.   \par \par \uc2 In the past two years or so, most of Indonesia's macroeconomic indicators have improved -- except for the unemployment rate -- as seen partly in the stable rupiah and easing inflation. But it has only helped drive the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth to a relatively stagnant 3 percent to 4 percent.   \par \par \uc2 Such growth is insufficient to absorb a net influx of 2.5 million people entering the job market annually, meaning that the country's unemployment rate has been increasing.   \par \par \uc2 Elsewhere, he said, another priority for the current \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  Cabinet team was to make sure that during the elections, which will take place from April to September, \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  activities will have to go on as much as normal as possible.   \par \par \uc2 "This also applies to the distribution of basic needs, which is very important to help maintain social stability during the elections from the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  side," he said.   \par \par \uc2 High also on the government's \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  agenda this year was the drawing up of the 2005 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  bill, which normally has to be submitted to the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  around August or September.   \par \par \uc2 "That will be our last \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  proposal. It is the task of the next government to deliberate the bill into a law," Dorodjatun said.   \par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020040105e01600008\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
