ue to a combination of \b \highlight22\uc2 economic uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2  at home and political jitters ahead of the July presidential election.  \par \par \uc2 Leo said that the rising gold price would cut trade volume of the commodity in the local market by around 50 percent in the coming months.  \par \par \uc2 In the last three months, the volume reached an average of 20 tons per month and might drop to 15 tons next month.  \par \par \uc2 A Pau, a gold shop owner in Cikini, Central Jakarta, also predicted that the price here would continue to increase.  \par \par \uc2 He was concerned, however, that the rising price would hurt business volume.  \par \par \uc2 He also hopes the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  and the government will take measures to help rescue the ailing rupiah.  \par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020040527e05s00015\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
