ion\b0 \highlight\uc2  system which is currently felt as complicated. The system should also become more transparent," he said.   \par \par \uc2 He also considered important that efforts to reduce bureaucratic costs, eradicate corruption, rehabilitate infrastructures and improve the financial sector.   \par \par \uc2 "In the financial sector, the government can privatize state banks and allow foreign banks to own them (the state banks)," he said.   \par \par \uc2 The government should also have a pro-market orientation and maintain the stability of central and regional policies, he added.   \par \par \uc2 Bakrie likewise saw the importance of law enforcement to protect the property ownership and give certainty of policies which provide opportunities to foreigners to manage plots of land more than 75 years.   \par \par \uc2 In an effort to convince domestic and foreign investors, the government should also guarantee a fair market competition, he said.   \par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020040614e06d0000x\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
